cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC 

This paper proposes a framework for task-oriented visual dialog systems that involves both reinforcement learning and supervised sequence-to-sequence models. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Among these categories, cs.CL and cs.CV are the most likely as they directly relate to the task of building a visual dialog system.
